features_zh: ['❄️ 作为一个迷你小冰箱：当炎炎夏日再次来临，您需要前往大学、办公室，甚至是卧室，我们的迷你冰箱总是必备的物品，可以用来冷藏饮料和水果。 这款卧室迷你冰箱的尺寸为17.83*16.73*19.8英寸，提供一个立方空间，可以存放从运动饮料到药物再到牛奶（顶部空间可放冰淇淋）的各种物品，可直接插入任何地方以节省空间。', '🥝 冰箱中的所有特色: 通过可拆卸玻璃隔板进行简单升级，让整理和清洁变得比以前更容易。小冰箱可逆门的特殊设计，适用于各种场合，方便双手使用。为了保护您的家具和地板免受刮擦，有2个可调节的腿，允许小冰箱水平放置，避免接触潮湿的地面。', '🥥 一键解冻设计: 你是否还在为手动解冻而苦恼？放弃吧！我们这款带有冷冻功能的小冰箱，在温度控制旋钮中间具有全新的一键解冻系统，能够帮助食物在几秒钟内融化。柔软可拆卸的门密封条不仅保护冰箱，还方便清洁。', '🥯 𝗦𝗔𝗩𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝗬𝗢𝗨𝗥 𝗕𝗜𝗟𝗟𝗦 𝗔𝗡𝗗 𝗞𝗘𝗘𝗣𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝗤𝗨𝗜𝗘𝗧: 由于可调节的恒温控制，从1（冷）到6（最冷），小冰箱提供了28.4-50℉的最佳温度范围，可储存水果和饮料，配备高效低耗能压缩机，为您省电费。无论您身在何处，带有冷冻功能的小冰箱运行顺畅，噪音最低37分贝以下，更好地融入任何空间。', '您的满意度是我们的首要任务：从我们的商店购买时是无风险的！如果您在收到我们的1.6立方冷藏箱时发现任何损坏零件，我们将为我们的客户提供100％的满意度保证。请首先与我们联系，如果您购买的产品未达到您的期望，我们将帮助您 :)']

title: 丹比 125.0L 黑色冰箱 DAR044A4BDD-6
features_en: ['Compact Mini Fridge: This Danby Designer counter high mini fridge is the ideal mini fridge for additional refrigerator space in the kitchen, basement, family room, dorm or office.Fresh Food Capacity: 4.4 cubic_feet', '4.4 Cubic Feet (124 Liters) Capacity: The All refrigerator unit is roomy with 4.4 cu. ft. of fridge space', 'Integrated Door Shelving: Tall bottle storage is ideal for large pop, water, juice, or other drink bottles', 'CanStor Beverage Dispensing System: Efficient and tidy can storage integrated into the mini refrigerator door', 'Clean Bright and Modern: White interior with bright interior lighting, wire shelves, integrated door handle and functional scratch resistant worktop', 'Fits anywhere: Smooth back design with no bulky exposed components means this small mini fridge can fit just about anywhere in your room', 'Versatile: Reversible door hinges, and 2 full width and 1 - 1/2 width adjustable wire shelves for undisrupted air circulation', 'Easy to Operate: Automatic defrost and mechanical thermostat means no extra maintenance on your part', 'Environmentally Friendly: Energy Star compliant and uses environmental-friendly R600a refrigerant']
description: ['The Danby Designer line of compact refrigerators is dedicated to being well built, easily maintained and convenient. The DAR044A4BDD-6 model features 4.4 cu. ft. (124 L) of cooling capacity making it the perfect fridge for spaces such as dormitory rooms, wet bars, rec-rooms, dens, workshops and basement lounges. Integrated door shelving with tall bottle storage makes storing all your additional drinks and snacks easy. Accessories can be stored on the scratch-resistant worktop and there’s no need to defrost the unit as it’s done automatically. This appliance also comes with a mechanical thermostat and offers 2.5 strong wire shelves for maximum storage versatility and optimal cool air circulation. Both left and right-handed users will love the convenient reversible door swing and the integrated door handle. This mini fridge is designed to blend with any decor style seamlessly.']

title: 楷模 125.0L 红色冰箱 99091
features_en: ['COMPACT MINI FRIDGE : Mini refrigerator and freezer has a total capacity of 4.4 cubic feet, and features a retro design to add vintage style to dorm rooms, offices, and garages', 'KEEP FOOD AND DRINKS COLD: With the mechanical temperature control, refrigerated food and beverages will be consistently kept cold and fresh', "CRISP, FRESH FOOD: Keep fruits and vegetables fresh with the clear crisper drawer, and allows quick access to your food items and makes it easy to spot what you're looking for", 'CHILLS QUICKLY: Separate cooling compartment is lower in temperature than the rest of the mini fridge, allowing you to cool items in a shorter time period', 'COMPACT FRIDGE DIMENSIONS: 19.3" W x 22.8" D x 36.1" H']
description: ['With the Kenmore 4.4 Cubic Feet Retro Compact Mini Fridge, you’ll be able to store excess food and drinks easily. The small refrigerator is portable and can be used at work under your desk, in the garage, or off at college in a dorm room. The retro mini fridge will add trendy vintage style to any room or living space. The thermostat lets you control the temperature with a simple turn of the knob. You’ll never have to worry about cold storage foods and drinks going bad. A separate chilling compartment gets items chilled in a hurry. Convenience features include adjustable glass shelves that can be removed to create customizable food storage and accommodate tall items and are also easy to clean. features_en: ['Compact Mini Fridge: This Danby Designer Mini Fridge is the perfect size to fit countertops, desktops or floor and is an ideal mini fridge for your bedroom, office, or dorm', '2.6 cubic feet (73 Liters) Capacity: The All refrigerator unit is small but mighty with 2.6 cu. ft. of fridge space', 'Integrated Door Shelving: Tall bottle storage is ideal for large pop, water, juice, or other drink bottles', 'CanStor Beverage Dispensing System: Efficient and tidy can storage integrated into the mini refrigerator door', 'Clean Bright and Modern: White interior, integrated door handle and functional textured scratch resistant worktop', 'Fits anywhere: Smooth back design with no bulky exposed components means this small mini fridge can fit just about anywhere in your room', 'Versatile: 2 full width and 1 - 1/2 width adjustable wire shelves for undisrupted air circulation and reversible door hinge', 'Easy to Operate: Automatic defrost and mechanical thermostat means no extra maintenance on your part', 'Environmentally Friendly: Energy Star compliant and uses environmental-friendly R600a refrigerant']
description: ['The Danby Designer line of compact refrigerators is dedicated to being well built, easily maintained and convenient. The DAR026A1WDD-6 model comes in at a height of just over two feet and features 2.6 cu. ft. (73 L) of cooling capacity. Quality can look good, with its sleek exterior, this is the ideal unit for floors and countertops, making it the perfect fridge for spaces such as dormitory rooms, wet bars, rec-rooms, dens, workshops and basement lounges. Integrated door shelving with tall bottle storage makes storing all your additional drinks and snacks easy. Accessories can be stored on the scratch-resistant worktop and there’s no need to defrost the unit as it’s done automatically. description: ['Product Description', "Forget running to the kitchen, enjoy the convenience of chilled beverages where they're needed most with our Energy Star rated Danby Designer compact all fridge. Boasting a generous capacity of 4.4 cu. ft. this counter high model is an efficient way to supplement your refrigerator. It includes our Canstor beverage dispenser, reversible door hinge and interior light.", 'From the Manufacturer', 'There’s no need to wear out a path to the kitchen every time you’re in the mood for a refreshing drink or snack. This compact, counter-high fridge by Danby is the ideal solution since it’s a perfect fit for any room in your home. It boasts a generous 4.4 cubic feet of cooling capacity and is outfitted with the popular CanStor beverage dispenser. Your electricity costs will be reduced due to the Energy-Star rating and highly-efficient mechanical thermostat. It uses R600a refrigerant to cool the interior. The white finish is easy to clean since it won’t smudge and the cycle defrosting system keeps it from freezing up. This spacious model offers two-and-a-half slide-out wire shelves along with a full-width door shelf and a pair of three-quarter-width door shelves for maximum storage room. There’s an attractive and functional clear vegetable crisper and cover inside along with a bright interior light for easy viewing. The integrated door handle ensures easy opening and the reversible door swing means it can be adjusted for either left or right-handed use. This stunning appliance also comes with 18-months coverage on parts and labor.']

features_en: ['Durable design built to last in outdoor kitchens', 'Designed for built-in undercounter installation in 24” wide settings', 'Stainless steel door includes keyed lock and pro handle', 'Deluxe interior with LED lighting, glass shelves, and a digital thermostat', 'Commercial grade design that meets NSF standards']
description: ['Summit Appliance offers a quality line of built-in all-refrigerators specially designed for user-friendly operation in outdoor settings. Model SPR627OS is a 24” wide all-refrigerator that can be used built-in or freestanding in any outdoor location. It comes with a jet black cabinet and a user-reversible stainless steel door equipped with a pro style handle and front lock. The sealed back design and ground fault circuit interrupter offer added safety from the elements in the outdoors. Frost-free operation ensures minimum maintenance, with digital controls for easy temperature management. Adjustable glass shelves offer easy storage, with a slotted floor that can safely hold bottles in place. Additional features include LED lighting and a Sabbath mode setting. The flat door liner is great for fitting deeper trays inside. The SPR627OS can be used in household or commercial settings. It is ETL-S listed to NSF-7 commercial standards and ENERGY STAR® certified as a commercial refrigerator.']

description: ["The Danby Health pharmaceutical refrigerator combines innovative technology and proven reliability demanded by medical and clinical facilities. This medical refrigerator is the ideal option for storing temperature sensitive goods. Featuring an internal forced air fan and wire shelves, cool air is evenly distributed and remains consistent. In addition, the integrated temperature logger measures the internal temperature every 10 minutes and stores the readings. This data is saved in a. CSV file and can be extracted via USB at your convenience. Product safety is easily regulated with it's high/low alarm, sounding when the temperature rises or falls outside the set range. Lastly, with its LED lighting and hospital grade power cord, this unit offers an all around professional look and performance."]

description: ['Product Description', 'You can add a touch of class to any room in your home or office with this striking compact refrigerator by Danby. It comes in at a height of just over two feet and features 2.6 cu. ft. (73 L) of cooling capacity. Finding storage room for tall bottles is no problem at all and the third-generation CanStor beverage dispenser is second to none. description: ['Having separate fridge and freezer refrigerators is definitely a great thing! You get that convenient combination and much more with this splendid dual-door compact refrigerator by Danby. This model offers 4.7 cu. ft. of cooling and freezing capacity and is Energy-Star compliant to help keep electricity costs as low as possible. The popular appliance is a perfect match for apartments, rec-rooms, bars, cottages and offices. It has a high-tech mechanical thermostat to make sure your foods are always stored at the correct temperature and has a handy cycle defrosting system. It comes with an intelligent reversible-door feature which allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. This glamorous fridge/freezer is a breeze to keep clean due to the stunning Black Stainless finish. Inside the appliance you’ll find a bright interior light as well as a see-through vegetable crisper with glass cover and plenty of space for tall bottles. The integrated door handle adds another touch of class. This highly-efficient appliance also features an 12 month warranty on parts and labor.']

Showcasing 1.7 cubic-feet (49 liters) of storage and cooling space, the cooler displays 1 1/2 tempered glass shelves and an integrated door shelving with tall bottle storage for optimal versatile storage. Also, enjoy an ideal place for your canned drinks with the included CanStor beverage dispensing system. The fridge's design beautifully incorporates a curved door design with a rubber-grip ergonomic handle that makes for a hassle-free user experience. Plus, place anything you want on the scratch-resistant worktop and experience the utmost energy efficiency with an environmentally-friendly R600a refrigerant. This refrigerator is Energy Star Compliant. Keep everything chill as can be with the Danby Compact Mini Fridge."]

description: ['Product Description', 'This apartment-sized refrigerator by Danby is second to none when it comes to performance and looks. This unit provides a generous 10 cubic feet (281 liters) of refrigeration space as well as a classy design that can fit in with any existing décor. The DFF100C1BSLDB features a convenient frost free-operation system. The appliance comes with three removable and adjustable glass shelves as well as a removable and adjustable wire shelf in the freezer compartment. It also provides a sizable vegetable crisper along with a glass cover. The unit can easily be programmed by its electronic controls with blue indication display and the handy reversible door hinge allows for both left and right-hand opening. If you prefer your drinks ice cold there’s an ice cube tray included and the bright white interior LED light makes it easy to see inside of the refrigerator compartment. This popular model also offers a 12-month warranty on parts and labor along with in-home service.', 'From the Manufacturer', 'The Danby DFF100C1BSLDB 9.9 Cu. Ft. Mid-Size Frost-Free Refrigerator with Top-Mount Freezer has spotless steel doors that look identical to real stainless steel without the smudging! With adjustable shelving, a sizable crisper drawer and frost free operation, this model is sure to fit all of your refrigeration needs. At just under 60 inches tall and less than 24 inches wide, the compact design is ideal for condos, apartments or as a secondary refrigerator/freezer.']

This compact refrigerator keeps drinks, snacks, small meals and skin care products ice cold, with a fun, retro-inspired design that infuses a little fun into everyday life. The Frigidaire mini fridge is built to last, using the same robust technology that's made Frigidaire one of the most trusted names in household appliances for nearly a century. It's designed with a powerful, whisper-quiet, vibration-free motor, harnessing dependable thermoelectric cooling. The unit cools down to 27-38 degrees Fahrenheit below ambient room temperature, keeping beverages at the optimal temperature. Two shelves allow for storing multiple items; a compact, see-through window makes it easy to monitor contents. Bold colors and a vintage logo enhance the nostalgia-inspired look and feel; the mini fridge can be plugged into a 12V car adapter or a standard outlet with included cords. Choose from multiple colors."]

features_zh: ['🥝用于办公室的 3.0 立方英尺 冷食储藏空间：如果您正在寻找完美的小型冰箱来保存新鲜水果、蔬菜或冷藏饮料，Frestec 小型办公室冰箱尺寸紧凑，为您保持所有需求的秩序和新鲜提供了满意。冰箱采用双门设计，我们的冰箱配有独立的 1 立方英尺冷冻区，足够宽敞，可以存放冰淇淋或在炎热夏季的冷冻食品。', '⚡ 保存您电费的省电冰箱：这款宿舍冰箱配备了高效低耗的R600压缩机，每天仅需消耗0.69度电和0.08美元，以保持食物内部的最佳湿度，比市面上大多数饮料冰箱的能耗更低。无论您身处何地，我们的迷你冰箱运转顺畅，噪音最低仅为37分贝，可完美安放在卧室、宿舍和办公室，不占用太多空间。', '▪️可调节温度控制: 这款黑色小冰箱配有手动可调节的恒温控制，从1（冷）到7（最冷），为您提供最佳的温度范围，可在不同季节或场合下，存放奶制品、蔬菜、水果和饮料，保持最佳状态。温度范围为 33.78-46.4℉。\n▪️4个可调节腿: 设有4个可调节腿，保护冰箱不受潮湿影响。', '❄️ 保持您的冰箱内部整洁无忧：无需再担心清洁冰箱的烦恼。这款带有冷冻室的紧凑冰箱配备了2个可拆卸玻璃板和一个玻璃货架，让您的食物有条不乱地组织存放更容易清理。LED照明使您可以在夜间轻松找到所需物品。特殊的可逆门设计友好地适应右撇子和左撇子用户。', '您的满意度是我们的首要任务：从我们的商店购买时无风险！如果您收到我们的3.0迷你冰箱有任何损坏零件，我们将为我们的客户提供100%的满意度保证。请您先联系我们，如果您购买的产品不符合您的期望，我们会帮助您 :)']

features_zh:
['**小型冰箱,配有双门双温区和大容量**: 17.83英寸（宽）*20.47英寸（长）*33.5英寸（高），这款节省空间的小型冰箱提供了3.0立方英尺的大容量（2.02立方英尺的冰箱区域，0.98立方英尺的冷冻区域），非常适合留在你的大学宿舍、房车、公寓、车库或办公室内，既可以存放你喜爱的饮料和食物，又占用最少的空间。双门设计与内部货架使你的食物井然有序。', '节能和静音技术：这款小冰箱符合能源之星标准。采用高效低耗散的压缩机，可以快速冷却食物。强大的压缩机每天只消耗0.7千瓦时，每天花费0.09美元，价格实惠且节能高效；工作时的小型冰箱噪音低于37分贝，非常适合那些需要安静居住和工作环境的人们。', "冷藏室选温迷你冰箱: 冷藏室区域可调节式7档温度控制，范围从23'到50'华氏度(1号位置是最冷，7号位置是最冷)，以满足不同蔬菜和水果的温度要求。顶部的冷冻室温度为-11.2～10.4°F，非常适合冰淇淋、海鲜、肉类等。", '体贴设计宿舍冰箱:

- 2 个可拆卸玻璃隔板，提供更多存储方式，满足您的需要。
- 1 个保鲜抽屉可减少果蔬水分流失，保持更长时间新鲜。
- LED 灯帮助您方便放置和取出食物。
- 复古样式的铬把手设计，唤起 1950 年代魅力。
- 可调节脚轮，提供更多灵活性。
- 可拆卸门密封圈，方便清洁冰箱。', '先进技术与质量保证 迷你冰箱：这款迷你冰箱配备先进压缩机，产生出色的冷却效果。增厚的泡沫和可拆卸的磁性密封条可防止冷空气泄漏，增强制冷效果。我们对产品质量充满信心，提供2年质量保证，如有任何问题，请随时与我们联系。']

features_zh: ['紧凑&大容量：4.7立方英尺的容量为您提供足够的空间来整理和存放冷冻食品。我们带有冷冻功能的小冰箱拥有更深更大的空间，尺寸为17.83 x 19.33 x 49.06英寸，大容量可让您的所有食物保持完全新鲜。', '7个可调温控：从21.2°F到-0.4°F，我们的小冰箱确保冷冻食物新鲜，存储最爱的冰淇淋。冰箱区域的温度范围为32°F到50°F，保持食材新鲜并锁住湿度。', '可移动的玻璃层板：冰箱内配有可移动的玻璃层板和金属层板，可以帮助您更好地组织物品。如果需要存放较高的物品，可以移除或调整层板以实现最大存储空间的需求，同时方便易取。', '静音运行：我们的小冰箱具有工程设计的静音压缩机，在启动和关闭时几乎无法被察觉。因此，这款带冷冻功能的冰箱非常适合宿舍、办公室、卧室、休息室、酒吧、车库和男性专属空间。', '准确搜索的自动灯光：由于内部照明自动点亮，食物的寻找变得简单，特别是在低光条件下打开冰箱门时，提供更方便的存储选项。']

features_en: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 18 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with a pre-installed ice maker is ENERGY STAR certified and provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable split shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items, while the utility bin offers easy-access to your favorite foods', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 29 7/8" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H with a 13.12 cubic ft. fresh food compartment and 5.07 cubic ft. freezer compartment for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic ft. of interior space and long-lasting LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features adjustable split shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh, while the utility bin provides easy access to your favorite foods. With the refrigerator\'s gallon-size door bins, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The convenient ice maker ensures your beverages stay cold, while the large, easy-to-grip handles make opening and closing the doors a breeze. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The ENERGY STAR certified fridge with energy efficient lighting meets EPA standards and can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a black finish measures 29 7/8" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 21 cubic ft. of interior space and long-lasting LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features full-width adjustable glass shelves to suit your food storage needs and 2 clear plastic crisper drawers to keep fruits and vegetables fresh. It also features slide-out glass storage shelves for easy access and removal of pies, cakes, casseroles, and larger food items. With the refrigerator\'s convenient door storage, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The gallon door bins make it easy to store tall items and beverages alongside your favorite sauces, condiments, and other ingredients. The tall item accommodation on the bottom shelf means more space for bottles of wine and water, while the convenient ice maker ensures your beverages stay cold out of the fridge as well. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized with two door bins and a single shelf. The 5.8 cubic ft. freezer also helps reduce freezer burn on your freezer and frozen food. The white refrigerator features a clean back design that hides the condenser coils, preventing the accumulation of dust and providing you with better performance. The ENERGY STAR certified fridge with energy efficient lighting meets EPA standards and can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator measures 33.8" x 32.87" x 66.1" for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

features_zh: ['🍥 3.2 𝐂𝐮.𝐅𝐓 为 𝐒𝐏𝐀𝐂𝐈𝐎𝐔𝐒 𝐒𝐓𝐎𝐑𝐈𝐍𝐆:\n如果您正在寻找一个完美的小冰箱来保存新鲜水果、蔬菜或冷藏饮料，这款 Frestec 迷你冰箱带冷冻室，紧凑尺寸为 17.8*20.5*33.5 英寸，能满足您保存所有食物需求并保持食物新鲜。这款我们卧室使用的双门设计小冰箱拥有一个独立的 1 立方英尺的冷冻区，空间足够宽敞，适合在炎炎夏日放置您的冰淇淋或冷冻食品。', '🍾 𝐒𝐀𝐕𝐈𝐍𝐆 𝐘𝐎𝐔𝐑 𝐄𝐋𝐄𝐂𝐓𝐑𝐈𝐂𝐈𝐓𝐘 𝐁𝐈𝐋𝐋:\n配备了R600高效低耗散的压缩机，这款宿舍冰箱每天只消耗0.69千瓦时和每天0.08美元来维持食物内部的最佳湿度水平，低于市场上大多数冰箱的能耗。无论您身在何处，我们的小型冰箱在卧室、宿舍和办公室中运行时噪音最低不超过37分贝，静音运行，不占用太多空间。', '❄️ 7档可调节温控功能: 手动可调节的温控功能可从1（冷）至7（最冷），我们的小冰箱为您提供了最佳的温度范围，存放奶制品、蔬菜、水果和饮料，在不同季节或场合保持最佳状态（33.78-46.4°F）。此外，还配备了2个可调节的脚，以防止冰箱潮湿。', '☀️ 冰箱中间的所有涂层: 不必担心清洁冰箱的麻烦。这款带有冷冻功能的紧凑冰箱配有2个可拆卸玻璃隔板和一个玻璃隔板，以满足您实际储存需求，轻松清洁。LED 照明使夜晚寻找所需的物品变得轻松。特殊的可逆门设计，方便右撇子和左撇子用户使用。', '💯 您的满意度是我们的首要任务：购买我们店铺的产品是零风险的！如果您收到我们的3.2升小冰箱时发现有任何损坏部件，我们将为我们的客户提供100%的满意保证。请联系我们并让我们知道，如果您购买的产品未达到您的期望，我们将帮助您 :)']

features_en: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR: 29.5 cu. ft. 4-door fridge and freezer provides ample fresh and frozen food storage and filters changed', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: 20.16 cubic feet of interior refrigerated space for fresh foods and 8.93 cubic feet of freezer storage, and has 5 gallon-size door bins for taller and wider food or beverage items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: 3 large flexible shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, and drawer style freezer holds all the frozen essentials', 'KEEPS FOODS FRESH: Triple Evaporator design creates separate cooling climates for the freezer, fridge, and ice compartments, while humidity controlled crispers ensure fresh fruits and veggies', 'ENERGY SAVING 4-DOOR REFRIGERATOR: French door refrigerator measures 35.87" W x 38.14" D x 68.82" H, and is ENERGY STAR certified']
description: ['The Kenmore 29.5 cu. ft. ENERGY STAR 4-Door Smart French Door Refrigerator offers plenty of fresh and frozen food storage, while providing your kitchen with a sleek and modern design. This fridge also features an Active Finish exterior ensuring it is easy to clean and fingerprint smudge resistant. With 20.16 cubic feet of interior refrigerated space and 8.93 cubic feet of freezer storage, you can stock up at the grocery store without running out of space. It also offers three large flexible shelves for customizable food storage that allows for easy access and removal of larger food and beverage items. Additional storage features, like five gallon-size door bins, allow you to store taller and wider food or beverage products. The drawer style freezer holds all of your frozen essentials, like pizzas, frozen meals, and ice cream. To keep foods fresh, the French door style fridge with freezer features a Triple Evaporator design that creates separate cooling climates for the freezer, refrigerator, and ice making compartments. The freezer has a dryer climate, while the fridge has a more humid climate. The humidity controlled crisper drawers keep your fruits and vegetables fresh, crisp, and delicious. This energy saving 4-door refrigerator/freezer combo features a French door style and measures 35.87" W x 38.14" D x 68.82" H, and is ENERGY STAR certified.']

features_zh:
['MINI REFRIGERATOR WITH 2 DOOR DUAL ZONE AND LARGE CAPACITY:
迷你冰箱，双门双温区，大容量
Dimensions: 17.83(W)" x 20.47(L)" x 33.5"(H)
尺寸：17.83英寸(宽) x 20.47英寸(长) x 33.5英寸(高)
This space saving small refrigerator provides 3.0 cu.ft large capacity
这款节省空间的小型冰箱提供了3.0立方英尺的大容量
(2.02 Cu.ft fridge area, 0.98 Cu.ft freezer area)
（2.02立方英尺的冷藏区域，0.98立方英尺的冷冻区域）
Perfectly sized to keep your favorite beverage and food while taking up minimal space in your college dorm, RV, apartment, garage or office.
完美的尺寸，可存放您喜爱的饮料和食物，同时仅占用您的大学宿舍、房车、公寓、车库或办公室的最小空间。
2 door design with inside racks make your food well organized
双门设计，内部架子使您的食物井井有条', '节能和静音技术：这款紧凑型冰箱符合能源之星标准。采用高效低耗的压缩机，能够快速冷却食物。强大的压缩机每天只消耗0.7千瓦时，每天成本为$0.09，经济实惠且节能；工作中的紧凑型冰箱噪音低于37分贝，非常适合那些对生活和工作环境要求安静的人们。', '选定温度宿舍尺寸冰箱：冰箱区7种设置可调节的恒温控制，范围从23°F到50°F（1位置最冷到7位置最凉），以满足不同蔬菜水果的温度要求。顶部冷冻室温度为-11.2°F到10.4°F，非常适合冰激凌、海鲜、肉类等。', '周到设计宿舍冰箱：
- 2个可拆卸玻璃板，更多方式整理储藏需求。
- 1个保鲜抽屉，减少水分流失，保持水果和蔬菜更加新鲜。
- LED灯，方便取放食物。
- 嵌入式手柄，使冰箱看起来精致现代。
- 可调节脚轮，提供极大的灵活性。
- 可拆卸门封，使清洁更加容易。', '先进技术&质量保证 迷你冰箱： 这款紧凑型冰箱配备了先进压缩机，产生出色的冷却效果。加厚泡沫和可拆卸的磁性密封条防止冷空气泄漏，增强制冷效果。我们对产品质量充满信心，我们提供2年质量承诺，如果您遇到任何问题，请随时与我们联系。']

features_zh: ['- 冷藏2门冷藏厨柜，双温区和大容量：17.83英寸(W) * 20.47英寸(L) * 33.5英寸(H)。这款节省空间的小型冰箱提供3.0立方英尺的大容量（2.02立方英尺的冰箱区域，0.98立方英尺的冷冻区域），尺寸完美，可在您的大学宿舍、房车、公寓、车库或办公室占用最少空间的情况下存放您最喜爱的饮料和食物。2门设计及内部架构使您的食物井然有序。', '节能和静音技术：这款紧凑型冰箱符合Energy Star标准。具有高效低耗的压缩机，可以快速冷却食物。强大的压缩机每天仅消耗0.7千瓦时，每天耗费0.09美元，价格实惠且节能高效；工作中的紧凑冰箱噪音低于37分贝，非常适合在生活和工作环境中需要安静的人们。', '小型冰箱选温：冰箱区域有7个设置可调节的恒温控制器，温度范围从23华氏度到50华氏度（1号位置最冷到7号位置最冷），满足不同蔬菜和水果的温度要求。顶部冷冻室温度为-11.2到10.4华氏度，非常适合冰淇淋、海鲜、肉类等食物。', '体贴设计宿舍冰箱：冰箱配有2个可移动玻璃架，提供更多的存储方式。1个保鲜抽屉可减少水分流失，使水果和蔬菜保持更长时间新鲜。LED灯可以帮助您轻松放置和取出食物。凹陷手柄使冰箱看起来精致和现代。可调节的脚轮提供极大的灵活性。可拆卸门封使清洁更加容易。', '先进技术&品质保证 迷你冰箱：这款小巧的冰箱配备了先进的压缩机，产生出色的冷却效果。加厚发泡层和可拆卸的磁性密封条防止冷气泄漏，并增强制冷效果。我们对产品质量充满信心，提供2年品质承诺，遇到任何问题请随时联系我们。']

description: ['Product Description', 'Having separate fridge and freezer units is definitely the way to go these days. You get that convenient combination and much more with this splendid dual-door compact refrigerator by Danby. This model offers 3.1 cu. ft. (87 L) of cooling and freezing capacity and is Energy-Star compliant to help keep electricity costs as low as possible. The popular appliance is a perfect match for apartments, rec-rooms, bars, cottages and offices. It has a high-tech mechanical thermostat to make sure your foods are always stored at the correct temperature and has a handy manual defrosting system. It comes with an intelligent reversible-door feature which allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. This glamorous fridge/freezer is a breeze to keep clean due to the stunning spotless-steel finish. Inside the appliance you’ll find a bright interior light as well as a see-through vegetable crisper with glass cover and plenty of space for tall bottles. The integrated door handle adds another touch of class.', 'From the Manufacturer', 'Having separate fridge and freezer units is definitely the way to go these days. You get that convenient combination and much more with this splendid dual-door compact refrigerator by Danby. This model offers 3.1 cu. ft. of cooling and freezing capacity and is Energy-Star compliant to help keep electricity costs as low as possible. It also uses environmentally friendly R600a refrigerant as the coolant for the unit. The popular appliance is a perfect match for apartments, rec-rooms, bars, cottages and offices. It has a high-tech mechanical thermostat to make sure your foods are always stored at the correct temperature and has a handy cycle defrosting system. It comes with an intelligent reversible-door feature which allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. This glamorous fridge/freezer is a breeze to keep clean due to the stunning spotless-steel finish. Inside the appliance you’ll find a bright interior light as well as a see-through vegetable crisper with glass cover and plenty of space for tall bottles. The integrated door handle adds another touch of class. This highly-efficient appliance also features an 18-month warranty on parts and labor.']

title: 楷模 515.0L 银色冰箱 70615
features_en: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 18 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with energy efficient LED lighting and pre-installed ice maker provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items.Frequency : 60 hertz', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable split shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items, while the utility bin offers easy-access to your favorite foods', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 29.76" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H with a 13.12 cubic ft. fresh food compartment and 5.07 cubic ft. freezer compartment for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic ft. of interior space and energy efficient LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features adjustable split shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh, while the utility bin provides easy access to your favorite foods. With the refrigerator\'s gallon-size door bins, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The large, easy-to-grip handles make opening and closing the doors a breeze. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The fridge can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors and comes with a built-in ice maker to keep your beverages cool. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a finger-print resistant stainless steel finish measures 29.76" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

features_en: ['Make the best use of space by installing your refrigerator under the counter', 'Approved for use in the outdoors, with a sealed exterior and double pane tempered glass door', 'Heat resistant design provides clear view of stored products, with an elegant trim in seamless stainless steel', 'Ideal for home wet bars, island kitchens, and other applications with limited footprint space', 'Three glass shelves with six positions for optimal storage and easy cleaning']
description: ['The SPR489OS features a versatile design that meets NSF-7 and UL-471 commercial standards, but is also approved for residential use. Sized at just 19 inches wide and 17 inches deep, it features a jet black cabinet with a sealed back for safe installation in the outdoors. The user-reversible double pane tempered glass door includes a seamless stainless steel trim and a pro style handle. A factory installed lock offers added security, while the space-saving right angle plug and integrated hinge provide added flexibility in unit placement. Two leveling legs keep the unit level on uneven surfaces. Inside, the SPR489OS utilizes an internal fan to ensure the interior is evenly cooled from top to bottom. An automatic defrost system allows for minimal user maintenance, while the white interior and LED lighting allows full visibility of stored items. Three adjustable glass shelves with six positions provide optimal storage capacity inside the 3.1 cu. ft. interior. The dial thermostat, with seven temperature settings, is located in the upper-right corner for easy temperature management.']

Stylish controls let you select temperatures with just a touch, keeping the inside cool while the party heats up. This unit is a convenient yet modern option for anyone looking to enhance their hosting space. With its sharp clean lines, this mini bar fridge is designed to blend with any decor style seamlessly."]
